Description: The first colour legally potted scoring its own value (i.e. not taken as a free ball).
Selections:
Yellow
Green
Brown
Blue
Pink
Black

Name: To Pot First Ball
Description: First player to pot a ball.

Name: To Pot Last Ball
Description: Last player to pot a ball.

Name: Century Break
Description: Will a century break be scored? A century break is a score of 100 points or more within one visit at the table without missing a shot.

Name: Player Century Break
Description: Will the named player score a century(100) break?

Name: Player 50+ Break
Description: Will the named player score a 50+ break?

Name: 50+ Break
Description: Will a 50+ break be scored?

Name: First Red Potted
Description: Which player will pot the first red?

Name: Team To Score Goal X
Description: The team to score goal X, if any.

Name: Team To Score Goal X With Money Back On No Goal
Description: The team to score goal X. If no goal X is scored, bets are refunded
Market Name: Team To Score Goal X With Money Back On No Goal

Name: Time Of Goal X
Description: The time (range) of the goal X to be scored, if any.

Name: Time Of Team Goal X
Description: The time (range) when the named team will score goal X, if any.

Name: Player To Score Goal X
Description: Who will score goal X, if any?

Name: Team To Score Try X
Description: The team to score try X, if any.

Name: Player To Score Try X
Description: Who will score xth try, if any?

Name: Asian Handicap With Score
Description: The winner of the remainder of the match, given a certain handicap. In case of a tie, the punter gets his money back. Only goals scored after the given score will count.

Name: Corner X
Description: The team to take the Xth corner kick, if any.

Name: Home Draw Away With Score
Description: Match result (home win, away win or draw) for the remainder of the match/event part. Only goals/points scored after the given score will count.

Name: Home Away With Score
Description: Match result (home wins, away wins) for the remainder of the match/event part. Only goals/points scored after the given score will count.

Name: Goal X Before Minute Y
Description: Will goal number X be scored before the specified minute?

Name: Team Goal X Before Minute Y
Description: Will the given team score goal number X before the specified minute?

Name: Team Runs Odd/Even In Xth Over
Description: Number of runs scored by the team in the specified Over is odd or even.

Name: Team Runs Over/Under In Xth Over
Description: Number of runs scored by the team in the specified Over is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Team Wicket In Xth Over
Description: Will a wicket fall in the specified Over? Team indicates the batting team.

Name: Team to Destroy Inhibitor X
Description: The team to destroy Inhibitor X, if any.

Name: Kills Handicap
Description: Team to get the most kills, given a certain handicap.

Name: Team to Score Kill X
Description: The team to score the xth kill, if any.

Name: Map Time Over/Under
Description: The match time is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Team Number Of Maps Won
Description: The number of maps won by the team.

Name: Maps Handicap
Description: Which team will win the most maps, given a certain handicap.

Name: Most Frags
Description: Team to get the most frags (frag= the difference between kills and deaths).

Name: Frags Handicap
Description: Which team will get the most frags, given a certain handicap (frag= the difference between kills and deaths).

Name: To Win by Elimination
Description: All the Counter-Terrorists were killed by the Terrorists team.

Name: To Win by Defused
Description: The planted bomb was successfully defused, therefore the Counter-Terrorists won the round.

Name: To Win by Bombed
Description: The planted bomb was successfully detonated, therefore the Terrorists won the round.

Name: To Win by Timeout
Description:
The round is won by 
 running out of time (i.e Terrorists were unable to plant the bomb, given a certain time).

Name: Rounds Odd/Even
Description: The number of rounds played is odd or even.

Name: Rounds Over/Under
Description: The number of rounds played is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Race To X Rounds
Description: First team to win X rounds.

Name: Round Handicap
Description: Which team will win the most rounds, given a certain handicap.

Name: Bomb Planted
Description: Will the Terrorists reach Counter's base and plant the bomb in that round?

Name: Headshots Over/Under
Description: The head shots number is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Team To Win Both Pistol Rounds
Description: Will the team win the pistol rounds? (there are 2 rounds per map, round 1 and round 16)

Name: Boxing Method Of Victory
Description: By which decision will the player win the match?

Name: Round Betting
Description: When (round x) or by which method will the winning player win the match?

Name: Grouped Round Betting
Description: When (round x-y) or by which method will the winning player win the match?

Name: Fight Result
Description: The method the match will be won by.

Name: Player To Score a Knockdown
Description: Will the named player score a knockdown?

Name: Player To be Knocked Down and Win
Description: The winning player has been knocked down and still won the match.

Name: Will Fight go the Distance?
Description: Will the match be decided after the normal time? (12 rounds)

Name: Double Result
Description: The winner of half time and full time, respectively.

Name: To Finish In Top Half
Description: To finish in the top half of the tournament.

Name: To Finish In Bottom Half
Description: To finish in the bottom half of the tournament.

Name: First Team To Score
Description: Team to score first in the competition.

Name: First Score Method 3 Way
Description: The scoring type of the first point(s) scored. By Touch Down, Field Goal or Any Other.

Name: First Score Method 6 Way
Description: The method the team scores the first point(s). Team By Touch Down, Field Goal or Any Other.

Name: Safety Scored
Description: Type of scoring play that was scored in the competition.

Name: Team Touchdowns Over/Under
Description: The number of touchdowns scored by a team is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: First Touchdown Scorer
Description: The first player to score a touchdown.

Name: Last Touchdown Scorer
Description: The last player to score a touchdown.

Name: Anytime Touchdown Scorer
Description: The player scores at least one touchdown.

Name: To Score x Or More Touchdowns
Description: Player to score X or more touchdowns.

Name: Team First Touchdown Scorer
Description: The team with the first touchdown scorer.

Name: Team Last Touchdown Scorer
Description: The team with the last touchdown scorer.

Name: First Quarter / Half Time
Description: The winner of the first quarter and half time, respectively.

Name: Top Nationality
Description: The winner of the competition played against adversaries with the same nationality.

Name: Player Passing Yards Over/Under
Description: The amount of yards gained by a player on completed passes is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Player Rush Yards Over/Under
Description: The amount of yards gained by a single player as the result of a rushing play is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: First Touchdown / Winner
Description: The player to score the first touchdown and the winner of the competition.

Name: Anytime Touchdown / Winner
Description: The player to score a touchdown and the winner of the competition.

Name: Matchflow
Description: Participant to score first and the match result: home, draw or away wins the match. Includes 'no goal'.

Name: Team Highest Scoring Event Part
Description: The part of the event with the highest number of points scored.

Name: Team To Make Substitution X
Description: The team to make the substitution number x.

Name: Double Chance & Both Teams To Score (6-way)
Description: Bet on 1X, X2 or 12 and both teams to score a goal.

Name: Double Chance & Over/Under
Description: Bet on 1X, X2 or 12 and on the end score being over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Matchbet & Team To Score Goal X
Description: Bet on the result of the match and home or away to score goal X, if any.

Name: Halftime Result & Both Teams To Score (6-way)
Description: Bet on the result of the first half and both teams to score a goal.

Name: Both Teams To Score And Totals (4-way)
Description: Bet on both teams to score or not and the end score being over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Matchbet And Both Teams To Score (6-way)
Description: Bet on the result of the match and both teams to score or not a goal.

Name: Action To Occur First (with cards)
Description: The action to occur first, if any (yellow card, goal, halftime whistle, red card, substitution)

Name: Score Draw
Description: Bet on the end score being draw or not.

Name: Goal Before X Minutes
Description: Will a goal be scored before x minutes of play?

Name: Goal After X Minutes
Description: Will a goal be scored after x minutes of play?

Name: Teams To Score
Description: Bet on both, neither, only home or only away team to score in the match.

Name: First 2 Points Of Game X Of Set Y
Description: Bet on the result after the first 2 points of a game, draw included.

Name: Double Result (1st Set/Match)
Description: Bet on the participant that will win the first set and the one that will win the match (1/1, 2/1, 1/2, 2/2)

Name: Any Set To Nil
Description: Bet on a participant to win a set and on the opponent being scoreless.

Name: Total Sets To Exceed The Score Limit
Description: Bet on the number of the sets that will exceed the score limit (i.e. for tennis is 6)

Name: Team To Slay Baron X
Description: The team to slay the xth baron, if any.

Name: Team To Slay Dragon X
Description: The team to slay the xth dragon, if any.

Name: Team To Slay Roshan X
Description: The team to slay the xth roshan, if any.

Name: Team To Destroy Tower X
Description: The team to destroy the xth tower, if any.

Name: Team To Slay Worker X
Description: The team to slay the xth worker, if any.

Name: Maps Odd/Even
Description: Will the total number of maps played be odd or even?

Name: Team To Win Round X
Description: Bet on the team to win the xth round, if any.

Name: Team To Destroy Barrack X
Description: Bet on the team to destroy the xth barack, if any.

Name: Godlike Streak
Description: Will there be a godlike streak in the match? (godlike reffers to the same player to score 9 kills without dying)

Name: Courier Kill
Description: Will there be a courier kill in the match?

Name: Kills Over/Under In Time Range
Description: Bet on the number of kills within a certain time range is over or under a certain threshold.

Name: First Active Rune Type
Description: Bet on the first active rune type (arcane, haste, invisibility, double damage, illusion, regeneration)

Name: Killing Spree Before Minute X
Description: Will there be a killing spree before minute X? (killing spree= same player scores 3 kills without dying)

Name: First Dragon Type
Description: Bet on the first dragon type (infernal, mountain, ocean, cloud) in a game of LOL.

Name: Largest Multi Kill
Description: Bet on the largest multi kill.

Name: Triple Kill
Description: Bet on a player to score a triple kill.

Name: Time of First Blood
Description: Bet on the time interval of the first blood.

Name: Time of First Tower Destroyed
Description: Bet on the time interval of the first tower destroyed.

Name: Highest Killing Spree Over/Under
Description: Bet on the highest killing spree to be over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Team Number Of Kills Over/Under
Description: Bet on the number of kills of a team to be over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Total Gold Over/Under
Description: Bet on the amount of gold to be over or under a certain threshold.

Name: Gold Handicap
Description: Bet on the team to have the higher amount of gold, given a certain handicap.

Name: Damage Handicap
Description: Bet on the team to have the higher amount of damage, given a certain handicap. In case of a tie, the punter gets his money back.
